    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Printed and hand-drawn maps and infographics showing the development of the campus and surrounding area. Contains maps for navigation or display as well as for providing additional information about campus. Includes map with information and statistics about the Cornell University Libraries.</p>  </scopecontent>
